      "title": "IMF delegation assures support for Sri Lanka",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "The visiting delegation of the International Monetary Fund (IMF) has assured President Gotabaya Rajapaksa that they would assist Sri Lanka in this crisis situation in compliance with the IMF\u2019s policies.",
        "The meeting between the IMF delegation and the Head of State took place at the President\u2019s House in Colombo this evening (June 24)."
